@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
@EndUserText.label: 'Ledger Company Information'
define root view entity ZETR_DDL_I_LEDGER_COMPANY_INFO
  as select from zetr_t_srkdb
{
  key bukrs       as CompanyCode,
      name1       as CompanyName1,
      name2       as CompanyName2,
      nace_code   as NaceCode,
      stcd1       as TaxId,
      stcd2       as TaxOffice,
      adress1     as Adress1,
      adress2     as Adress2,
      house_num   as HouseNum,
      postal_code as PostalCode,
      city        as City,
      country_u   as CountryU,
      tel_number  as TelNumber,
      fax_number  as FaxNumber,
      email       as Email,
      web         as Web,
      legal       as Legal,
      creator     as Creator,
      branch_type as BranchType,
      days45      as Days45,
      rldnr       as Ledger,
      ablart      as OpenningDocType,
      kblart      as ClosingDocType,
      hdatab      as LedgerStartDate,
      hdatbi      as LedgerEndDate,
      tastar      as LiquidationDate,
      maxit       as MaxItem,
      maxcr       as MaxCursor ,
      intid       as Entegrator,
      srapi       as ApiAdress,
      sausr       as ApiUser,
      sapas       as ApiPass,
      desti       as ApiDestination,
      ktopl       as ChartOfAcc,
      tosys       as SendDataToOtherSystem,
      frsys       as GetDatafromOtherSystem,
      sm59_dest   as Sm59Dest,
      no_part     as NoPart
}
